{"tid":1469980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比意見唔等如割蓆呀屌你老母","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:26:29.000Z","uid":194959,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07f897a6b791d4195dd5b7aadd5839ca54531465","tid":1469980,"uid":194959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"一直以嚟都話兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n一直以嚟冇大台<br />\n所以唔同意見同一目標嘅人<br />\n都可以喺呢個運動入面共存<br />\n<br />\n幾時開始有啲人接受唔到其他人嘅意見呀？<br />\n你可以唔聽，但點解直接屌比意見嘅人割蓆？<br />\n係同你割蓆嘅話我理撚得你去死？仲比咩意見？<br />\n唔通大家覺得而加運動好完全唔需要改進？<br />\n<br />\n813有人早啲人就比人屌散水撚<br />\n814有人比意見就比人屌割蓆撚<br />\n呢個運動幾時變到只係可以有一個方法去支持<br />\n只可以容納一種聲音？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母醒吓啦分化撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbfd3f70bfae93c2e15417de59a2a06a3199d602","tid":1469980,"uid":14214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"因為勇武大晒<br />\n勇武=大台"},{"pid":"f7d2b67192fd7931bb276d97c0e2b9f988ff1f28","tid":1469980,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"（長文）仲記唔記得咩叫兄弟爬山同不割𥱊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3d3cbcf178d746158c05cb30b3f76bf31766f66","tid":1469980,"uid":194959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4437e60db84b8e867c03c2f1d2f3751be8e44fda","tid":1469980,"uid":194959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"070b28c6c1fec3514a00268500264d70ca57233d","tid":1469980,"uid":194142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"而家D人好惡&hellip;有時侯比D意見 就話分化同5毛........"},{"pid":"73f7d07e931f29c1c6dcabd9cdcfc3554c16b6f2","tid":1469980,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"去現場屌唔該"},{"pid":"b272fcdc3